. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM waffle fabric for a textured, premium feel. Oversized fit for a relaxed and comfortable silhouette. Raglan sleeves for improved movement and fit. Front embroidered logo with back silicone print for durability and style. Unisex design suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for superior softness and long-la\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064570232986,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064570265754,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064570298522,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47064570331290,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064570364058,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47064570396826,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00602copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440553"},{"product_id":"fear-no-one-waffle","title":"FEAR NO ONE - WAFFLE","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Waffle Knit Fabric. Baggy Fit with Knit Collar. Front \u0026amp; Back Vinyl Prints. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 240 GSM waffle knit collar tee from Drip Studios blends structure with a relaxed, baggy silhouette for an elevated everyday look. Crafted from premium waffle fabric, it offers breathable comfort with a rich texture and lasting softness. The front features the Drip Signature Number 9 in high-quality vinyl print, keeping the design bold yet refined, while the back makes a powerful statement with “FEAR NO ONE” in durable vinyl printing. Finished with a knit collar for a clean, polished touch, this tee is combed and bio-washed to ensure superior comfort, shape retention, and long-term wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash inside out with similar colors using cold water. Do not bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain fabric quality and vinyl prints. Avoid direct ironing on prints. Store folded in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM premium waffle knit fabric for a textured, breathable feel. Perfect baggy fit for a relaxed yet structured silhouette. Knit collar for a clean and elevated finish. Front Drip Signature Number 9 vinyl print with bold “FEAR NO ONE” back print. High-quality vinyl printing for durability and sharp detailing. Unisex design suitable for all body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for enhanced softness and longevity.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47079248724122,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":47079248756890,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079248789658,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47079248822426,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079248855194,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47079248887962,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00346copy_11zon_1.jpg?v=1771440357"}],"url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/collections\/new-arrivals.oembed","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}